      "source": [
        "假設班上10位同學的數學成績是90,80,88,84,85,87,88,89,90,100,請建立一個score串列來儲存學生成績。\n",
        "\n",
        "1.請幫第一位同學成績加10分\n",
        "\n",
        "2.請幫最後一位同學成績減10分\n",
        "\n",
        "3.印出最後的串列"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "CaW8pGCOc_YJ"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 1,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "ti30aVpscmgH",
        "outputId": "f90b39a7-5556-4fae-8b74-7d0d65f6f629"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "新的成績 [100, 80, 88, 84, 85, 87, 88, 89, 90, 90]\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "score=[90,80,88,84,85,87,88,89,90,100]\n",
        "score[0]=score[0]+10\n",
        "score[-1]=score[-1]-10\n",
        "print('新的成績',score)"
      ]
    }
